{"type": "article", "id": 27560, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28341, "name": "Iris"}, {"id": 28342, "name": "Neo/Craft"}, {"id": 28343, "name": "Equals Design"}, {"id": 28344, "name": "LEAFXPRO"}, {"id": 28345, "name": "ByFutura"}, {"id": 28346, "name": "Joseph Joseph"}, {"id": 28347, "name": "Mon Choco"}, {"id": 28348, "name": "Sebastian Scherer"}, {"id": 28349, "name": "Paul Farrell"}, {"id": 28350, "name": "Dae-hoo Kim"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142438nNGBmo8ESKjRT49w.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Iris by Sebastian Scherer</h2>\n<p>还记得小时候和朋友一起玩吹泡泡的游戏吗，你是否想过把美丽的泡泡们留住？Sebastian Scherer 为 Neo/Craft 设计的吊灯 <a href=\"http://en.neocraft.com/product/iris/\">Iris</a> 是一款获得 2016 德国设计奖的作品，Scherer 以肥皂泡作为灵感，采用纯人工吹制的方法制作而成。为了还原出泡泡在阳光下的颜色，Iris 内部附着了一层彩虹膜，光线透过灯罩时就会产生奇妙的光影变化。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121640WNfm8SQ2DJ4URwu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121640JdwZaBRozuGr37VK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070212164130Kk8YMfcIRWjo9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216412iI8Pw7UrWZ4fvdh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Zoo Clocks by Paul Farrell</h2>\n<p>英国设计师 Paul Farrell 最近推出了一个动物园时钟系列，包含了五种不同动物的木质时钟。Farrell 以抽象的动物脸部图案作为钟面，并且通过动物的花纹表示刻度，非常可爱。这是挂钟的<a href=\"http://www.byshop.co/shop/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 48.30 英镑（<a href=\"http://www.byshop.co/shop/bjorn-polar-bear-clock\">白熊款</a>为 48.39 英镑）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216429Zk1zU4jDShadlOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121642fgS83pIVUMnRYWQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216439ma1S4irb2GMKuTe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121643BIC1lo8ew4mEguhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121644zxsSiImuht9kbMTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216444dOK69cmp0gNEi8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Volcano by Dae-hoo Kim</h2>\n<p>谁说水火一定不容？韩国设计师 Dae-hoo Kim 以火山喷发为灵感，设计了这款火山造型的加湿器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/8875721/VOLCANO\">Volcano</a>。它的造型非常简洁，四种不同的外观分别对应了来自世界各地的知名火山，使用时只需要将水倒入“火山口”即可。除了普通的喷气模式之外，这款火山加湿器还有一个模仿火山喷发的“喷烟圈”模式，这个时候“火山口”还会配合亮起红色的灯光，非常形象。这款产品目前还未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121645gd5MfRbHPOV81NWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121646JoPU6XOhC892IgDT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121646C4TUpM981LAfmEZF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121646bdRqP1KEfVij0X8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216474jJSNWT0CD7srAQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121649B3zjaL8bVFW1h5Jd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Shake-It by Equals Design</h2>\n<p>为了帮助人们在厨房中解放双手，加快料理速度，Equals Design 为厨具品牌 <a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-us/\">Joseph Joseph</a> 设计了一款可以单手掌控的过滤器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/37362481/Joseph-Joseph-Shake-it-Self-Tapping-Sieve\">Shake-It</a>。它的设计非常简洁，塑料套固定住了过滤器的金属把手，只需要单手摇晃就可以使面粉落下，这个时候你就可以同时进行搅拌了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-us/shake-it\">购买链接</a>，售价为 17 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121649mdyLVhJP3lGbYzjg.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57777778\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121650htSDWerAzlbUBpX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121650rD6HcGvnQqdwJpVg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121651NPMTCRUhkltZVi45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>LEAFXPRO 2 by LEAFXPRO team</h2>\n<p>即使是下雨天也可以舒舒服服地骑着自行车出行——LEAFXPRO 团队的设计师们以此为理念设计出了一款专门为自行车设计的雨伞，这一次他们带来了产品的升级版。LEAFXPRO 2 的造型根据空气动力学研发，能够在恶劣的天气情况下能保证骑行的顺畅，而且组装起来也非常简单。除了本体之外，LEAFXPRO 2 还提供了两款可选配件，一件是可以保护骑手身体两侧的防雨罩，另一件则专门为罩住后座儿童椅而设计，家长们也不用担心孩子会淋湿了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/leafxpro-2-bicycle-every-day--4#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 49 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121651jqYNQ4cAO6CtRUkr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70483871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121652qOsCdcPRMSUlGLn7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3225\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121652OwDTR5MugJpcHq82.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121653HptMi9SIRNTgzEeZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216549FfiRSIe5x3aHM7g.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61204013\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121655BHQfovtsn3rkJYmu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mon Choco by ByFutura</h2>\n<p>这一系列配色清新的包装由 <a href=\"http://byfutura.com/project/mon-choco/\">ByFutura</a> 为科特迪瓦的巧克力品牌 Mon Choco 所设计。为了凸显出产品均在当地手工制作而成，他们绘制了一套人们在可可园劳作的场景图作为主要元素使用，在为生产溯源的同时也表达了对土地的敬意。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121656bejFvsWzAVKhI8iL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121657vT1iACsx9uSUeY3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121657tnrLj4U8ciGYuhIW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121658Y71ZgRPCdcTtpKbm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121658xfaYzN30QMdokZq9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121658ZBj4SAI3rMl9oqp5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}